OL,3,CBrixton shooting: Four people in
OL,4,Chospital after shots fired from vehicle
OL,6,FFour people are in hospital ` one in a
OL,7,Flife-threatening condition ` after
OL,8,Fmultiple shots were fired from a
OL,9,Fvehicle in Brixton, south London.
OL,11,FPolice were called around 1.15am on
OL,12,FSaturday, May 2, following reports of
OL,13,Fa shooting on Coldharbour Lane,
OL,14,FBrixton.
OL,16,FOfficers were on the scene within four
OL,17,Fminutes and provided emergency first
OL,18,Faid alongside the London Ambulance
OL,19,FService.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
