OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1777842664
OL,3,CBrixton shooting: Four people in
OL,4,Chospital after shots fired from vehicle
OL,6,FFour people were taken to hospital
OL,7,Fwith gunshot wounds ` one of whom, a
OL,8,F25-year-old man, remains in a life-
OL,9,Fthreatening condition.
OL,11,FThree others ` aged 21, 47 and 70 `
OL,12,Fhave been assessed and their injuries
OL,13,Fhave been deemed not life-threatening
OL,14,For life-changing.
OL,16,FA London Ambulance Service
OL,17,Fspokesperson said that two people were
OL,18,Ftaken to a major trauma centre and the
OL,19,Fother two to a local hospital, with a
OL,20,Ftrauma team from London's Air
OL,21,FAmbulance joining ambulance crews.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
