OL,3,CBrixton shooting: Four people in
OL,4,Chospital after shots fired from vehicle
OL,6,FNo arrests have been made yet and
OL,7,Fdetectives are appealing for help from
OL,8,Fthe public to find those responsible
OL,9,Ffor the shooting.
OL,11,FLeading the investigation, Detective
OL,12,FChief Inspector Allam Bhangoo said:
OL,13,F"We understand how concerning this
OL,14,Fincident will be for the local
OL,15,Fcommunity and want to reassure
OL,16,Fresidents that officers are working at
OL,17,Fpace to identify those responsible.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
