OL,3,CBrixton shooting: Four people in
OL,4,Chospital after shots fired from vehicle
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"This was an act of indiscriminate
OL,12,Fviolence, and we will work
OL,13,Frelentlessly to bring the suspects to
OL,14,Fjustice.
OL,16,F"It is vital that anyone who witnessed
OL,17,Fthe incident, or has information that
OL,18,Fcould assist the investigation, comes
OL,19,Fforward.
OL,26,@sD@AOUxD@AOU
