OL,3,CBrixton shooting: Four people in
OL,4,Chospital after shots fired from vehicle
OL,6,F"Local residents can expect to see an
OL,7,Fincreased police presence in the area
OL,8,Fover the coming days. If you have any
OL,9,Fconcerns, please speak to officers.
OL,11,FAnyone with information or footage
OL,12,Fthat could assist police has been
OL,13,Fasked to contact 101, quoting CAD 557/
OL,14,F2May.
OL,16,FAlternatively, information can be
OL,17,Fprovided anonymously via the
OL,18,Findependent charity Crimestoppers on
OL,19,F0800 555 111.
